725139f-a.title: Queens: 24th Road - 21st Street
725139f-a.text:
24th Road (foreground, not shown), east of 21st Street (left, not
shown), showing Fairbanks' old water tower (erected by Ed. Woolsey)
in back of old 41 Cedar Place (now 24th Road). In the background are
seen the rears of homes facing on TYwenty-fourth Ave.
1922.
Eugene L. Ambruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
